io.github.msdk.io.mgf

Class MgfMsSpectrum

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.msdk.datamodel.AbstractMsSpectrum
      • io.github.msdk.io.mgf.MgfMsSpectrum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MsSpectrum

    public class MgfMsSpectrum
extends AbstractMsSpectrum

    MgfMsSpectrum class.

    This class extends AbstractMsSpectrum and stores additional fields title - name of the spectrum precursor ion charge and mass level - MsLevel of the spectrum (1 or 2)
